			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Check out <a title="Lean UX" href="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/2011/03/07/lean-ux-getting-out-of-the-deliverables-business/" target="_blank">this great article</a> on Smashing Magazine on Lean UX, a methodology rooted in Agile.</p>
<p>Excerpt:</p>
<blockquote><p>&#8220;Inspired by Lean and Agile development theories, Lean UX is the practice of bringing the true nature of our work to light faster, with less emphasis on deliverables and greater focus on the actual experience being designed.&#8221;</p></blockquote>
